entries.femaleVariant: He was choking on his own blood, you know? He was all blue, thrashing, screaming like… like an animal.
We tried, but what can you do… they shut down his implants, that was that.
Kate said he worked for Petrochem.
Yeah. Corp just flipped the switch, no warning. Lungs, legs… Christ, even his eyes.
Wasn't that the guy in charge of the Argentina contract?
